IN RE: GUARDIANSHIP OF W.P., Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-3820 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. November 30, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Upon consideration of petitioner's response to this court's order to show cause dated October 31, 2018, the petition for writ of certiorari is dismissed as moot.

BLACK, SLEET, and ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, JJ., Concur.
